data.description: Motivated sellers! Come tour this stunning property located in the highly desirable Trails neighborhood!  This home features beautiful updates throughout, including engineered hardwood floors (no carpet), a large eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a walk-in pantry with lots of storage & more. The large primary bedroom suite is located on the lower level and features a full-size shower, separate soaking tub, double sink vanity, and a spacious walk-in closet.  The additional 3 bedrooms located on the 2nd level each offer walk-in closets ideal for extra storage and are joined by an oversized loft. The property is backed up to open space nature trails with no immediate neighbors in the back and is equipped with a Vivint power purchase solar system that keeps your PNM bill low.
